----------------------------------------------------------------------
Blank filing forms (NOT redistributed)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The blank PDF forms this library maps are public records of the Maine
Secretary of State, Bureau of Corporations, Elections and Commissions:

    https://www.maine.gov/sos/cec/corp

They are NOT included in or redistributed by this repository. Each form's
entry in catalog/pdf_manifest.json carries the official source URL, a byte
size, and a SHA-256, which lets the tooling fetch and verify the official
blank on demand (see tools/fetch_pdfs.py).

The forms remain public records of the State of Maine; this project claims
no rights over them. Any built artifact that embeds a blank Maine Secretary
of State form should carry this attribution.

This repository's own work — code (engine/, tools/) and the structured form
artifacts (forms/<ID>/ metadata, schemas, mappings, skills, rubrics;
catalog/; docs/) — is the part licensed under Apache-2.0.

Not legal advice. Filled output is a draft and must be verified against the
official form, and against current Maine law, before filing.
